Tomcat is http server and servlet container.Even we can run jsp becuase internally jsp will be converted to servlet.Apcahe tomcat is free.
Other servers available are jetty.
Glassfish,JBOSS are application servers.
For enterprise application we use application server whereas webserver provides web environment for servlets,jsp,html
Superior is application server which provides support for servlets,jsp,html,jms,ejb.
Application server automatically has inbuilt webserver.We need to install webserver separatley if you are not satisfied with application server which has web server.
Web application can be developed using web relatedtechnologies like servlets,jsp,html,css.
Entreprise application can be developed using java/jee,ejb,jms
